  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Sutakomi: Star Communicator is a game by Konami based on traditional pet-raising style games, such as Tamagotchi. The player takes care of a cute \"Star Communicator\", raising them into adulthood before sending them out into the world to work a job.This title also supported the Mobile GB Adapter which allowed players to send and receive mail online, buy items for the pet, and paid content was also used in a \"Star Marriage\" feature where two players could marry their pets to each other.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
